{"key":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01|1Ch|25","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Ch","chapter":25,"textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024","parserRevision":"v10","verses":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:25:1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Ch","bookOrder":12,"chapter":25,"verse":1,"text":"David and the officers of the army also set apart some of the sons of Asaph, Heman, and Jeduthun, who were to prophesy accompanied by lyres, harps, and cymbals. This is the list of the men who performed their service:","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:25:2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Ch","bookOrder":12,"chapter":25,"verse":2,"text":"From Asaph’s sons:","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:25:3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Ch","bookOrder":12,"chapter":25,"verse":3,"text":"From Jeduthun: Jeduthun’s sons:","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:25:4","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Ch","bookOrder":12,"chapter":25,"verse":4,"text":"From Heman: Heman’s sons:","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:25:5","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Ch","bookOrder":12,"chapter":25,"verse":5,"text":"All these sons of Heman, the king’s seer, were given by the promises of God to exalt him, for God had given Heman fourteen sons and three daughters.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:25:6","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Ch","bookOrder":12,"chapter":25,"verse":6,"text":"All these men were under their own fathers’ authority for the music in the Lord’s temple, with cymbals, harps, and lyres for the service of God’s temple. Asaph, Jeduthun, and Heman were under the king’s authority.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:25:7","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Ch","bookOrder":12,"chapter":25,"verse":7,"text":"They numbered 288 together with their relatives who were all trained and skillful in music for the Lord.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:25:8","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Ch","bookOrder":12,"chapter":25,"verse":8,"text":"They cast lots for their duties, young and old alike, teacher as well as pupil.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:25:9","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Ch","bookOrder":12,"chapter":25,"verse":9,"text":"The first lot for Asaph fell to Joseph, his sons, and his relatives — 12","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:25:10","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Ch","bookOrder":12,"chapter":25,"verse":10,"text":"the third to Zaccur, his sons, and his relatives — 12","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:25:11","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Ch","bookOrder":12,"chapter":25,"verse":11,"text":"the fourth to Izri, his sons, and his relatives — 12","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:25:12","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Ch","bookOrder":12,"chapter":25,"verse":12,"text":"the fifth to Nethaniah, his sons, and his relatives — 12","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:25:13","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Ch","bookOrder":12,"chapter":25,"verse":13,"text":"the sixth to Bukkiah, his sons, and his relatives — 12","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:25:14","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Ch","bookOrder":12,"chapter":25,"verse":14,"text":"the seventh to Jesarelah, his sons, and his relatives — 12","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:25:15","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Ch","bookOrder":12,"chapter":25,"verse":15,"text":"the eighth to Jeshaiah, his sons, and hi